# 🛍️ FashonStore

A Java Web E-Commerce application built using Java Servlets, JSP, JDBC, MySQL, and Maven.

## 🚀 Features

* User Registration and Login
* Product Listing and Details
* Shopping Cart
* Checkout Process
* Order Confirmation
* MySQL Database Integration
* Session Management

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* Java
* JSP
* Servlets
* JDBC
* MySQL
* Maven
* Apache Tomcat
* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript

