## ⚙️ Prerequisites

* Java 21 or later
* Maven 3.9+
* MySQL 8+
* Apache Tomcat 10+

## 🔧 Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/sonukrishna054/FashonStore.git
```

### Navigate to Project Folder

```bash
cd FashonStore
```

### Build Project

```bash
mvn clean install
```

### Run Application

Deploy the generated WAR file to Apache Tomcat and open:

```text
http://localhost:8080/FashonStore
```

